                            <comment id="12745914" author="fmeschbe" created="Fri, 21 Aug 2009 11:45:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In Rev. 806106 &quot;moved&quot; the &quot;official&quot; implementation of the ComponentInstance interface to the ComponentContextImpl class. Instances of this class are recreated whenever the component is activated. This ensures the ComponentInstance contract which has the same lifecycle requirement as the ComponentContext.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
